These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, marigold, tulip, rose
1. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsiris and the person who growsmarigold##2
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Flower   | iris | rose | marigold | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, tram, skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Transport   | tram | jet-ski | bike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, dunhill, blend, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
2. the alhambra-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the blend-smoker is between the chaman-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar   | alhambra | chaman | blend | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, september, june
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
2. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in september##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Birthday   | october | august | june | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, july, may
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | may | june | july | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking, magic-tricks, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | reading | drawing | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, satire, zombie
