2. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching epic movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | comedy | satire | epic |

