.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-11::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, strawberry, pineapple, spinach
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
2. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
3. the person eating carrot is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating spinach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | spinach | carrot | pineapple | strawberry |

