.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
City: san-francisco, hamburg, berlin, paris
1. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to berlin is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| City   | hamburg | berlin | san-francisco | paris |

