.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, fish, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
4. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Pet   | fish | chinchilla | rabbit | mouse |

