.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, september, july
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | september | july | march | january |

